111Kg 7:5 All the doorways and doorposts had rectangular frames, with the doorways facing each other in three tiers. 
111Kg 7:6 There was also a hall of pillars 75 feet long and 45 feet wide, and a porch in front with pillars, and a canopy in front of the pillars. 
