142Ch 25:16 But even while the prophet was speaking, the king asked him, "Did we appoint you to be a royal counselor?Stop! Why should you be struck down?" So the prophet stopped speaking, but he also said, "I know God has determined to destroy you, because you've done all this and ignored my counsel."
